These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, sailing
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | sailing | parkour | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: papaya, zucchini, strawberry
1. the person eating zucchini is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | papaya | strawberry | zucchini |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | woodworking | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, pop, trance
1. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | trance | pop |

 #################################

 
